{"tid":221726,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"M痛坐關愛座被中年婦「搞小動作」讓座：關愛座唔係刻左你個名","createTime":"2017-04-29T02:21:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-29T05:37:09.000Z","uid":93753,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0c563de26e2f87dd092ac6191ef8862d896edec6","tid":221726,"uid":93753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T02:21:33.000Z","msg":"早前70歲婦偷影中學生指責不讓座事件鬧得熱烘烘，網友都再次強調讓座是人情，而非道理，而且有很多年輕人身體狀況不佳，比健康的老人家更需要被讓座。<br />\n<br />\n有年輕女生在Facebook群組發帖，指搭港鐵時沒有位置坐，因生理期不適而坐關愛座。卻被一位中年婦搞小動作，暗示讓座。內文指中年婦盯著她看，整個車程不斷吹氣，令到口水都噴到樓主臉上。指對方肺活量好，似乎不是有需要人士。這樣出位地要求讓座令人很不舒服。指「其實關愛座真係唔係刻左你個名。」<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U3291Pu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU3291Pu.png&h=8bde7251&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/topic/detail.html?id=ABFGD1owBwhZFgNt&amp;p=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Ftopic%2Fdetail.html%3Fid%3DABFGD1owBwhZFgNt%26p%3D2&d=awVbgeYyyy76%2F43Y8QfwzpUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=6e06c793\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/topic/detail.html?id=ABFGD1owBwhZFgNt&amp;p=2</a><br />\n<br />\n廢老 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9669c734ff2f99f79a5aa52ab358554fba43444","tid":221726,"uid":112494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T02:23:48.000Z","msg":"一向唔理 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecb667cde23c7210c3232f26416d42e2c92de832","tid":221726,"uid":91176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T02:24:56.000Z","msg":"諗關愛座出來個個同啲廢老一樣咁on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67cfcb9e3bb7542c62acac4017c0c69408b84dbb","tid":221726,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T02:28:59.000Z","msg":"想坐咪出聲囉<img src=\"